<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Gestión de Citas - Citas Médicas</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap 5 & Icons -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <!-- Estilos compartidos -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/app.css">
        <script src="/js/mobile-toggle.js" defer></script>
    <script>
        (function() {
            const t = localStorage.getItem('theme');
            if (t === 'dark') {
                document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', 'dark');
                document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-bs-theme', 'dark');
            }
            const c = localStorage.getItem('color-theme') || 'clinico';
            document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-color-theme', c);
        })();
    </script>
    <!-- FullCalendar CDN -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/fullcalendar@6.1.8/index.global.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/fullcalendar@6.1.8/index.global.min.js" defer></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/fullcalendar@6.1.8/locales/es.global.min.js" defer></script>
    <!-- SweetAlert2 -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@11"></script>
    
    <style>
        /* Ajustes específicos para la página de citas */

        /* Tabs de navegación con estilos premium consistentes con el diseño de 8px */
        .nav-pills .nav-link {
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-weight: 550;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
        }

        .nav-pills .nav-link:hover {
            color: var(--color-primary);
            background-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.05);
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] .nav-pills .nav-link:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        }

        .nav-pills .nav-link.active {
            background-color: var(--color-primary);
            color: #ffffff;
            border-color: var(--color-primary);
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] .nav-pills .nav-link.active {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            color: #ffffff;
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        /* FullCalendar: Integración con la paleta de colores y bordes del sistema */
        #calendar {
            background-color: var(--surface-color);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            padding: 15px;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .fc-header-toolbar {
            margin-bottom: 1.25em !important;
        }

        .fc-toolbar-title {
            font-size: 1.25rem !important;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Botones de FullCalendar */
        .fc .fc-button-primary {
            background-color: var(--surface-color) !important;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color) !important;
            color: var(--text-main) !important;
            font-size: 0.85rem !important;
            font-weight: 550 !important;
            padding: 6px 12px !important;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius) !important;
            box-shadow: none !important;
            text-transform: capitalize;
            transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
        }

        .fc .fc-button-primary:hover {
            background-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.05) !important;
            border-color: var(--color-primary) !important;
            color: var(--color-primary) !important;
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] .fc .fc-button-primary:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05) !important;
            border-color: var(--border-hover) !important;
            color: #ffffff !important;
        }

        .fc .fc-button-active {
            background-color: var(--color-primary) !important;
            border-color: var(--color-primary) !important;
            color: #ffffff !important;
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] .fc .fc-button-active {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08) !important;
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) !important;
            color: #ffffff !important;
        }

        .fc .fc-button-primary:disabled {
            background-color: var(--surface-color) !important;
            border-color: var(--border-color) !important;
            color: var(--text-muted) !important;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        /* Bordes y Grilla del Calendario */
        .fc-theme-standard td, 
        .fc-theme-standard th, 
        .fc-theme-standard .fc-scrollgrid {
            border-color: var(--border-color) !important;
        }

        .fc-col-header-cell {
            background-color: rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.02);
            padding: 8px 0 !important;
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] .fc-col-header-cell {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);
        }

        .fc-col-header-cell-cushion {
            color: var(--text-muted) !important;
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .fc-daygrid-day-number {
            color: var(--text-main) !important;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            padding: 6px !important;
        }

        .fc-daygrid-day.fc-day-today {
            background-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.04) !important;
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] .fc-daygrid-day.fc-day-today {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02) !important;
        }

        /* Eventos del Calendario */
        .fc-event {
            border-radius: 4px !important;
            padding: 2px 4px !important;
            font-size: 0.78rem !important;
            font-weight: 550;
            border: none !important;
        }

        /* Pulsing Dot for Live Chat */
        .nav-link .badge-dot {
            background: #f43f5e;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            margin-left: auto;
            animation: pulse 1.5s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
            50% { opacity: .5; transform: scale(1.3); }
        }

        /* Ajustes FullCalendar y Layout en Móviles */
        @media (max-width: 767.98px) {
            #calendar {
                padding: 8px;
            }
            .fc-toolbar-title {
                font-size: 1rem !important;
            }
            .fc .fc-button-primary {
                padding: 4px 8px !important;
                font-size: 0.75rem !important;
            }
            .fc-header-toolbar {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 8px;
                align-items: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">            <!-- Sidebar Navigation -->
            <div class="col-md-2 sidebar p-0 d-flex flex-column d-none d-md-flex">
                <div class="p-4 brand-title d-flex align-items-center gap-2 mb-3">
                    <i class="bi bi-hospital fs-4" style="color:#818cf8"></i>
                    <span class="fs-5">Citas Médicas</span>
                </div>
                <nav class="nav flex-column">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/dashboard"><i class="bi bi-grid-1x2"></i> Dashboard</a>
                    <a class="nav-link active" href="/citas"><i class="bi bi-calendar3"></i> Citas</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/pacientes"><i class="bi bi-people-fill"></i> Pacientes</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/mensajes"><i class="bi bi-chat-left-dots-fill"></i> Mensajes</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/chat"><i class="bi bi-chat-dots-fill"></i> Chat en Vivo <span class="badge-dot ms-auto" id="unread-dot" style="display:none"></span></a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/analytics"><i class="bi bi-bar-chart-line-fill"></i> Analytics</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/configuracion"><i class="bi bi-gear-fill"></i> Configuración</a>
                </nav>

                <!-- WhatsApp Status Widget -->
                <div class="wa-status-widget mx-2 mt-3">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                        <span class="wa-dot off" id="ws-status-icon"></span>
                        <span class="fw-semibold small text-main">WhatsApp Bot</span>
                    </div>
                    <div id="ws-status-text" class="small text-muted">Consultando...</div>
                    <div id="ws-qr-container" class="mt-2 text-center d-none">
                        <img id="ws-qr-img" src="" alt="Escanee QR" class="img-fluid rounded" style="max-height:120px">
                        <div class="small mt-1 text-warning">📱 Escanee para conectar</div>
                    </div>
                    <button onclick="reconectarWA()" class="btn btn-sm w-100 mt-2">
                        <i class="bi bi-arrow-repeat me-1"></i>Reconectar
                    </button>
                </div>

                <div class="px-3 py-2 mt-auto mb-2">
                    <button class="btn-sidebar-action mb-2 animate-hover" onclick="toggleDark()">
                        <i class="bi bi-moon-fill" id="dark-icon"></i> Modo Oscuro
                    </button>
                    <a href="/logout" class="btn-sidebar-action btn-sidebar-danger animate-hover">
                        <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-left"></i> Cerrar Sesión
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Main Content Area -->
            <div class="col-md-10 main-content">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4 pb-2 border-bottom">
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="fw-bold mb-1">Gestión de Citas</h2>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-0">Listado y calendario de todas las consultas médicas</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-inline-flex gap-2">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger text-white d-inline-flex align-items-center" onclick="abrirModalEmergencia()"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill me-1"></i> <span class="d-none d-md-inline">Reportar Emergencia</span><span class="d-inline d-md-none">Emergencia</span></button>
                        <a href="/api/citas/exportar-csv" class="btn btn-outline-success d-none d-md-inline-flex"><i class="bi bi-file-earmark-spreadsheet me-1"></i> Exportar CSV</a>
                        <a href="/citas/nueva" class="btn btn-primary text-white"><i class="bi bi-calendar-plus me-1"></i> <span class="d-none d-sm-inline">Nueva Cita</span><span class="d-inline d-sm-none">Nueva</span></a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Tabs header & content -->
                <div>
                    <ul class="nav nav-pills mb-4" id="citasTabs" role="tablist">
                    <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                        <button class="nav-link active" id="listado-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab" data-bs-target="#listado-tab-pane" type="button" role="tab"><i class="bi bi-list-task me-1"></i> Listado de Citas</button>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                        <button class="nav-link" id="calendario-tab" data-bs-toggle="tab" data-bs-target="#calendario-tab-pane" type="button" role="tab"><i class="bi bi-calendar-range me-1"></i> Calendario Visual</button>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <div class="tab-content" id="citasTabContent">
                    <!-- Tab Listado -->
                    <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="listado-tab-pane" role="tabpanel" tabindex="0">
                        
                        <!-- Filtros de Búsqueda -->
                        <div class="card mb-4">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <form method="GET" action="/citas" class="row g-3">
                                    <div class="col-md-3">
                                        <label for="buscar" class="form-label small fw-semibold text-muted">Buscar</label>
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-sm" id="buscar" name="buscar" placeholder="Paciente, teléfono, motivo..." value="<%= (typeof filtros !== 'undefined' && filtros.buscar) ? filtros.buscar : '' %>">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-3">
                                        <label for="estado" class="form-label small fw-semibold text-muted">Estado</label>
                                        <select class="form-select form-select-sm" id="estado" name="estado">
                                            <option value="">Todos</option>
                                            <option value="pendiente" <%= (typeof filtros !== 'undefined' && filtros.estado === 'pendiente') ? 'selected' : '' %>>⏳ Pendiente</option>
                                            <option value="confirmada" <%= (typeof filtros !== 'undefined' && filtros.estado === 'confirmada') ? 'selected' : '' %>>✅ Confirmada</option>
                                            <option value="cancelada" <%= (typeof filtros !== 'undefined' && filtros.estado === 'cancelada') ? 'selected' : '' %>>❌ Cancelada</option>
                                            <option value="reagendada" <%= (typeof filtros !== 'undefined' && filtros.estado === 'reagendada') ? 'selected' : '' %>>🔄 Reagendada</option>
                                        </select>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-2">
                                        <label for="fecha_desde" class="form-label small fw-semibold text-muted">Desde</label>
                                        <input type="date" class="form-control form-control-sm" id="fecha_desde" name="fecha_desde" value="<%= (typeof filtros !== 'undefined' && filtros.fecha_desde) ? filtros.fecha_desde : '' %>">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-2">
                                        <label for="fecha_hasta" class="form-label small fw-semibold text-muted">Hasta</label>
                                        <input type="date" class="form-control form-control-sm" id="fecha_hasta" name="fecha_hasta" value="<%= (typeof filtros !== 'undefined' && filtros.fecha_hasta) ? filtros.fecha_hasta : '' %>">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-2 d-flex align-items-end gap-2">
                                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary w-100"><i class="bi bi-filter"></i> Filtrar</button>
                                        <a href="/citas" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary w-100">Limpiar</a>
                                    </div>
                                </form>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body p-0">
                                <% if (citas.length > 0) { %>
                                    <!-- Vista Desktop (Tabla) -->
                                    <div class="table-responsive d-none d-md-block">
                                        <table class="table table-hover">
                                            <thead>
                                                <tr>
                                                    <th>ID</th>
                                                    <th>Paciente</th>
                                                    <th>Teléfono</th>
                                                    <th>Fecha</th>
                                                    <th>Hora</th>
                                                    <th>Motivo</th>
                                                    <th>Estado</th>
                                                    <th>Calificación</th>
                                                    <th>Notas</th>
                                                    <th class="text-end">Acciones</th>
                                                </tr>
                                            </thead>
                                            <tbody>
                                                <% citas.forEach(cita => { %>
                                                    <tr>
                                                        <td class="text-muted">#<%= cita.id %></td>
                                                        <td class="fw-semibold"><%= cita.paciente_nombre %></td>
                                                        <td><i class="bi bi-whatsapp text-success me-1"></i> <%= cita.paciente_telefono %></td>
                                                        <td><%= new Date(cita.fecha + 'T00:00:00').toLocaleDateString('es-ES') %></td>
                                                        <td class="fw-semibold text-primary"><%= cita.hora %></td>
                                                        <td><span class="text-muted"><%= cita.motivo %></span></td>
                                                        <td>
                                                            <% if (cita.estado === 'confirmada') { %>
                                                                <span class="badge bg-success"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill me-1"></i> Confirmada</span>
                                                            <% } else if (cita.estado === 'cancelada') { %>
                                                                <span class="badge bg-danger"><i class="bi bi-x-circle-fill me-1"></i> Cancelada</span>
                                                            <% } else if (cita.estado === 'reagendada') { %>
                                                                <span class="badge bg-info text-dark"><i class="bi bi-arrow-repeat me-1"></i> Reagendada</span>
                                                            <% } else { %>
                                                                <span class="badge bg-warning text-dark"><i class="bi bi-clock-fill me-1"></i> Pendiente</span>
                                                            <% } %>
                                                        </td>
                                                        <td>
                                                            <% if (cita.calificacion) { %>
                                                                <span class="text-warning fw-semibold">
                                                                    <% for(let i=0; i<cita.calificacion; i++) { %>★<% } %>
                                                                    <span class="text-muted small">(<%= cita.calificacion %>)</span>
                                                                </span>
                                                            <% } else if (cita.estado === 'confirmada') { %>
                                                                <span class="text-muted small">Pendiente encuesta</span>
                                                            <% } else { %>
                                                                <span class="text-muted small">-</span>
                                                            <% } %>
                                                        </td>
                                                        <td>
                                                            <% if (cita.notas) { %>
                                                                <span class="text-muted small" title="<%= cita.notas %>"><%= cita.notas.length > 25 ? cita.notas.substring(0, 22) + '...' : cita.notas %></span>
                                                            <% } else { %>
                                                                <span class="text-muted small">-</span>
                                                            <% } %>
                                                        </td>
                                                        <td class="text-end">
                                                            <div class="d-inline-flex gap-2">
                                                                <a href="/citas/<%= cita.id %>/editar" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary" style="padding: 6px 10px; border-radius:8px;">
                                                                    <i class="bi bi-pencil"></i>
                                                                </a>
                                                                <form action="/citas/<%= cita.id %>/eliminar" method="POST" style="display: inline;" onsubmit="return confirm('¿Estás seguro de eliminar esta cita?')">
                                                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-danger" style="padding: 6px 10px; border-radius:8px;">
                                                                        <i class="bi bi-trash"></i>
                                                                    </button>
                                                                </form>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </td>
                                                    </tr>
                                                <% }); %>
                                            </tbody>
                                        </table>
                                    </div>

                                    <!-- Vista Móvil (Tarjetas) -->
                                    <div class="d-block d-md-none p-3">
                                        <% citas.forEach(cita => { %>
                                            <% 
                                                let borderClass = 'border-warning'; // pendiente
                                                let badgeClass = 'bg-warning text-dark';
                                                let statusText = 'Pendiente';
                                                if (cita.estado === 'confirmada') { 
                                                    borderClass = 'border-success'; 
                                                    badgeClass = 'bg-success';
                                                    statusText = 'Confirmada';
                                                } else if (cita.estado === 'cancelada') { 
                                                    borderClass = 'border-danger'; 
                                                    badgeClass = 'bg-danger';
                                                    statusText = 'Cancelada';
                                                } else if (cita.estado === 'reagendada') { 
                                                    borderClass = 'border-info'; 
                                                    badgeClass = 'bg-info text-dark';
                                                    statusText = 'Reagendada';
                                                }
                                            %>
                                            <div class="card mb-3 p-3 border-start border-4 <%= borderClass %>" style="border-radius: 8px;">
                                                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start mb-2">
                                                    <div>
                                                        <span class="text-muted small">#<%= cita.id %></span>
                                                        <h6 class="fw-bold text-main mb-1" style="font-size: 0.95rem;"><%= cita.paciente_nombre %></h6>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <span class="badge <%= badgeClass %>"><%= statusText %></span>
                                                </div>
                                                
                                                <div class="my-2 small text-muted">
                                                    <div class="mb-1"><i class="bi bi-calendar-event me-2 text-primary"></i><strong>Fecha:</strong> <%= new Date(cita.fecha + 'T00:00:00').toLocaleDateString('es-ES') %></div>
                                                    <div class="mb-1"><i class="bi bi-clock me-2 text-primary"></i><strong>Hora:</strong> <span class="fw-semibold text-primary"><%= cita.hora.substring(0, 5) %></span></div>
                                                    <% if (cita.motivo) { %>
                                                        <div class="mb-1"><i class="bi bi-clipboard2-pulse me-2"></i><strong>Motivo:</strong> <%= cita.motivo %></div>
                                                    <% } %>
                                                    <% if (cita.notas) { %>
                                                        <div class="mb-1 text-truncate" title="<%= cita.notas %>"><i class="bi text-muted bi-chat-left-text me-2"></i><strong>Notas:</strong> <%= cita.notas %></div>
                                                    <% } %>
                                                    <% if (cita.calificacion) { %>
                                                        <div class="mb-1"><i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning me-2"></i><strong>Calificación:</strong> 
                                                            <span class="text-warning fw-semibold">
                                                                <% for(let i=0; i<cita.calificacion; i++) { %>★<% } %>
                                                                <span class="text-muted small">(<%= cita.calificacion %>)</span>
                                                            </span>
                                                        </div>
                                                    <% } %>
                                                </div>

                                                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mt-3 pt-2 border-top border-light">
                                                    <div class="small">
                                                        <i class="bi bi-whatsapp text-success me-1"></i>
                                                        <a href="/chat?phone=<%= cita.paciente_telefono %>" class="text-decoration-none text-main fw-semibold"><%= cita.paciente_telefono %></a>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="d-flex gap-2">
                                                        <a href="/citas/<%= cita.id %>/editar" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary px-2 py-1" style="border-radius: 6px;" title="Editar">
                                                            <i class="bi bi-pencil"></i>
                                                        </a>
                                                        <form action="/citas/<%= cita.id %>/eliminar" method="POST" style="display: inline;" onsubmit="return confirm('¿Estás seguro de eliminar esta cita?')">
                                                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-danger px-2 py-1" style="border-radius: 6px;" title="Eliminar">
                                                                <i class="bi bi-trash"></i>
                                                            </button>
                                                        </form>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        <% }); %>
                                    </div>
                                <% } else { %>
                                    <div class="text-center py-5 text-muted">
                                        <i class="bi bi-calendar-x fs-1 opacity-50"></i>
                                        <p class="mt-2 mb-3">No hay citas médicas registradas en la base de datos.</p>
                                        <a href="/citas/nueva" class="btn btn-primary text-white"><i class="bi bi-calendar-plus me-1"></i> Agendar Primera Cita</a>
                                    </div>
                                <% } %>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Tab Calendario -->
                    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="calendario-tab-pane" role="tabpanel" tabindex="0">
                        <div class="card p-4">
                            <div id="calendar"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap Bundle -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

    <!-- Dark Mode & SSE script -->
    <script>
        // Dark Mode Toggle
        function toggleDark() {
            const html = document.documentElement;
            const isDark = html.getAttribute('data-theme') === 'dark';
            const nextTheme = isDark ? '' : 'dark';
            html.setAttribute('data-theme', nextTheme);
            html.setAttribute('data-bs-theme', nextTheme === 'dark' ? 'dark' : 'light');
            
            const icon = document.getElementById('dark-icon');
            if (icon) {
                icon.className = isDark ? 'bi bi-moon-fill' : 'bi bi-sun-fill';
                const parent = icon.parentElement;
                if (parent) {
                    parent.innerHTML = isDark
                        ? '<i class="bi bi-moon-fill" id="dark-icon"></i> Modo Oscuro'
                        : '<i class="bi bi-sun-fill" id="dark-icon"></i> Modo Claro';
                }
            }
            localStorage.setItem('theme', isDark ? 'light' : 'dark');
        }
        if (localStorage.getItem('theme') === 'dark') {
            document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', 'dark');
            document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-bs-theme', 'dark');
            document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
                const icon = document.getElementById('dark-icon');
                if (icon) {
                    icon.className = 'bi bi-sun-fill';
                    const parent = icon.parentElement;
                    if (parent) {
                        parent.innerHTML = '<i class="bi bi-sun-fill" id="dark-icon"></i> Modo Claro';
                    }
                }
            });
        }

        async function reconectarWA() {
            try {
                await fetch('/api/whatsapp/reconectar', { method: 'POST' });
            } catch (e) {}
        }

        // Fetch unread chat count & SSE status
        async function loadUnreadCount() {
            try {
                const res = await fetch('/api/chat/no-leidos');
                const data = await res.json();
                const dot = document.getElementById('unread-dot');
                if (dot) {
                    dot.style.display = data.count > 0 ? 'inline-block' : 'none';
                }
            } catch (err) { console.error('Error fetching unread count:', err); }
        }
        loadUnreadCount();

        // Connect to SSE for real-time status and unread messages
        const sseConn = new EventSource('/api/updates/live');
        sseConn.addEventListener('wa_status', e => {
            const d = JSON.parse(e.data);
            const dot = document.getElementById('ws-status-icon') || document.getElementById('wa-dot');
            const text = document.getElementById('ws-status-text') || document.getElementById('wa-text');
            const qrContainer = document.getElementById('ws-qr-container');
            const qrImg = document.getElementById('ws-qr-img');
            
            if (dot && text) {
                if (d.status === 'conectado') {
                    dot.className = 'bi bi-circle-fill text-success wa-dot on';
                    text.innerText = 'Conectado (Listo)';
                    if (qrContainer) qrContainer.classList.add('d-none');
                } else {
                    dot.className = 'bi bi-circle-fill text-danger wa-dot';
                    text.innerText = `Desconectado (${d.status})`;
                    if (d.qrCode && qrContainer) {
                        qrImg.src = d.qrCode;
                        qrContainer.classList.remove('d-none');
                    } else if (qrContainer) {
                        qrContainer.classList.add('d-none');
                    }
                }
            }
        });
        sseConn.addEventListener('mensaje', e => {
            const d = JSON.parse(e.data);
            if (d.remitente === 'paciente') {
                const dot = document.getElementById('unread-dot');
                if (dot) dot.style.display = 'inline-block';
            }
        });

        sseConn.addEventListener('cita', e => {
            console.log('🔔 Cambio en citas detectado. Recargando...', e.data);
            window.location.reload();
        });

        window.addEventListener('beforeunload', () => {
            if (sseConn) sseConn.close();
        });
    </script>

    <!-- FullCalendar initialization script -->
    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            var calendarEl = document.getElementById('calendar');
            var calendar = new FullCalendar.Calendar(calendarEl, {
                initialView: 'dayGridMonth',
                locale: 'es',
                editable: true,
                headerToolbar: {
                    left: 'prev,next today',
                    center: 'title',
                    right: 'dayGridMonth,timeGridWeek,timeGridDay'
                },
                eventDrop: async function(info) {
                    const citaId = info.event.id;
                    const props = info.event.extendedProps;
                    
                    const newStart = info.event.start;
                    const yyyy = newStart.getFullYear();
                    const mm = String(newStart.getMonth() + 1).padStart(2, '0');
                    const dd = String(newStart.getDate()).padStart(2, '0');
                    const fecha = `${yyyy}-${mm}-${dd}`;
                    
                    const hh = String(newStart.getHours()).padStart(2, '0');
                    const min = String(newStart.getMinutes()).padStart(2, '0');
                    const hora = `${hh}:${min}:00`;

                    // Mostrar indicador de carga premium
                    Swal.fire({
                        title: 'Procesando reprogramación',
                        text: `Moviendo la cita de ${props.paciente}...`,
                        icon: 'info',
                        allowOutsideClick: false,
                        showConfirmButton: false,
                        didOpen: () => { Swal.showLoading(); }
                    });

                    try {
                        const response = await fetch(`/api/citas/${citaId}/reprogramar`, {
                            method: 'POST',
                            headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
                            body: JSON.stringify({ fecha, hora })
                        });
                        const resData = await response.json();
                        
                        if (resData.success) {
                            Swal.fire({
                                icon: 'success',
                                title: '¡Cita Reprogramada!',
                                html: `La cita de <strong>${props.paciente}</strong> se ha reprogramado correctamente:<br><br>📅 <strong>${dd}/${mm}/${yyyy}</strong> a las ⏰ <strong>${hh}:${min} hrs</strong>`,
                                timer: 4000,
                                showConfirmButton: true,
                                confirmButtonColor: '#4f46e5'
                            });
                        } else {
                            throw new Error(resData.error || 'Error al reprogramar en servidor');
                        }
                    } catch (error) {
                        console.error('Error al reprogramar la cita:', error);
                        Swal.fire({
                            icon: 'error',
                            title: 'Error de Reprogramación',
                            text: 'No se pudo actualizar la cita en la base de datos. Se revertirá el cambio.',
                            confirmButtonColor: '#ef4444'
                        });
                        info.revert();
                    }
                },
                events: [
                    <% citas.forEach(cita => { 
                        let color = '#eab308'; // amarillo (pendiente)
                        if (cita.estado === 'confirmada') color = '#22c55e'; // verde
                        if (cita.estado === 'cancelada') color = '#ef4444'; // rojo
                        if (cita.estado === 'reagendada') color = '#06b6d4'; // cian
                    %>
                    {
                        id: '<%= cita.id %>',
                        title: '<%= cita.paciente_nombre.replace(/'/g, "\\'") %> - <%= cita.motivo ? cita.motivo.replace(/'/g, "\\'") : "Consulta" %>',
                        start: '<%= cita.fecha %>T<%= cita.hora %>',
                        color: '<%= color %>',
                        textColor: '#ffffff',
                        extendedProps: {
                            paciente: '<%= cita.paciente_nombre.replace(/'/g, "\\'") %>',
                            telefono: '<%= cita.paciente_telefono %>',
                            motivo: '<%= cita.motivo ? cita.motivo.replace(/'/g, "\\'") : "Consulta" %>',
                            estado: '<%= cita.estado %>'
                        }
                    },
                    <% }); %>
                ],
                eventClick: function(info) {
                    const props = info.event.extendedProps;
                    let estadoBadge = '<span class="badge bg-warning text-dark">Pendiente</span>';
                    if (props.estado === 'confirmada') estadoBadge = '<span class="badge bg-success">Confirmada</span>';
                    if (props.estado === 'cancelada') estadoBadge = '<span class="badge bg-danger">Cancelada</span>';
                    if (props.estado === 'reagendada') estadoBadge = '<span class="badge bg-info text-dark">Reagendada</span>';

                    const startStr = info.event.startStr;
                    let fechaHoraDisplay = '';
                    if (startStr.includes('T')) {
                        const [f, h] = startStr.split('T');
                        const [yyyy, mm, dd] = f.split('-');
                        fechaHoraDisplay = `${dd}/${mm}/${yyyy} a las ${h.substring(0, 5)} hrs`;
                    } else {
                        const [yyyy, mm, dd] = startStr.split('-');
                        fechaHoraDisplay = `${dd}/${mm}/${yyyy}`;
                    }

                    const modalContent = `
                        <div class="modal fade" id="calendarEventModal" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
                            <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
                                <div class="modal-content" style="border-radius: var(--border-radius);">
                                    <div class="modal-header">
                                        <h5 class="modal-title fw-bold">Detalle de la Cita</h5>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="modal-body">
                                        <p class="mb-2"><strong>Paciente:</strong> ${props.paciente}</p>
                                        <p class="mb-2"><strong>Teléfono:</strong> +${props.telefono}</p>
                                        <p class="mb-2"><strong>Fecha/Hora:</strong> ${fechaHoraDisplay}</p>
                                        <p class="mb-2"><strong>Motivo:</strong> ${props.motivo}</p>
                                        <p class="mb-0"><strong>Estado:</strong> ${estadoBadge}</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="modal-footer">
                                        <a href="/citas/${info.event.id}/editar" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm text-white">Editar Cita</a>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Cerrar</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    `;
                    
                    const oldModal = document.getElementById('calendarEventModal');
                    if (oldModal) oldModal.remove();

                    document.body.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', modalContent);
                    var modal = new bootstrap.Modal(document.getElementById('calendarEventModal'));
                    modal.show();
                }
            });
            
            const tabEl = document.getElementById('calendario-tab');
            tabEl.addEventListener('shown.bs.tab', function () {
                calendar.render();
            });
        });

        function abrirModalEmergencia() {
            const hoyStr = new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0];
            document.getElementById('emg-fecha').value = hoyStr;
            document.getElementById('emg-razon').value = '';
            var myModal = new bootstrap.Modal(document.getElementById('emergenciaModal'));
            myModal.show();
        }

        async function confirmarEmergencia() {
            const fecha = document.getElementById('emg-fecha').value;
            const razon = document.getElementById('emg-razon').value;

            if (!fecha) {
                Swal.fire({ icon: 'error', title: 'Error', text: 'Selecciona una fecha.' });
                return;
            }

            const result = await Swal.fire({
                title: '¿Confirmar Emergencia?',
                text: 'Esta acción cancelará todas las citas confirmadas/pendientes de este día y enviará un aviso de WhatsApp a los pacientes. No se puede deshacer.',
                icon: 'warning',
                showCancelButton: true,
                confirmButtonColor: '#ef4444',
                cancelButtonColor: '#6c757d',
                confirmButtonText: 'Sí, cancelar y notificar',
                cancelButtonText: 'Cancelar'
            });

            if (result.isConfirmed) {
                try {
                    Swal.fire({
                        title: 'Procesando...',
                        html: 'Cancelando citas y encolando avisos de WhatsApp...',
                        allowOutsideClick: false,
                        didOpen: () => { Swal.showLoading(); }
                    });

                    const res = await fetch('/api/emergencia/cancelar-reagendar', {
                        method: 'POST',
                        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
                        body: JSON.stringify({ fecha, razon })
                    });
                    const data = await res.json();
                    
                    if (res.ok && data.success) {
                        Swal.fire({
                            icon: 'success',
                            title: 'Proceso completado',
                            text: `Se cancelaron y notificaron ${data.count} citas correctamente.`
                        }).then(() => {
                            window.location.reload();
                        });
                    } else {
                        Swal.fire({ icon: 'error', title: 'Error', text: data.error || 'Ocurrió un error.' });
                    }
                } catch (e) {
                    Swal.fire({ icon: 'error', title: 'Error', text: 'Error al enviar petición.' });
                }
            }
        }
    </script>

    <!-- Modal Reportar Emergencia (Cancelar y Reagendar) -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="emergenciaModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="emergenciaModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content" style="border-radius: var(--border-radius); background-color: var(--surface-color); color: var(--text-main); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
                <div class="modal-header border-bottom-0 pb-0">
                    <h5 class="modal-title fw-bold text-danger" id="emergenciaModalLabel"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-octagon-fill me-2"></i> Reportar Emergencia</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p class="text-muted small">Esto cancelará todas las citas activas de la fecha seleccionada y enviará notificaciones por WhatsApp a los pacientes afectados permitiéndoles reagendar.</p>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="emg-fecha" class="form-label fw-semibold">Fecha a Cancelar</label>
                        <input type="date" class="form-control" id="emg-fecha" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="emg-razon" class="form-label fw-semibold">Motivo / Razón de la cancelación</label>
                        <textarea class="form-control" id="emg-razon" rows="3" placeholder="Ej. un imprevisto médico de fuerza mayor"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer border-top-0 pt-0">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Cerrar</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm text-white" onclick="confirmarEmergencia()">Enviar Avisos y Cancelar</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
